jn_uOsL-Egabdfyxp9CeKyRtdnBvbO1N_wVy3SBBGVdxq26DObni60LYQgV7YxpcxxUWgiVBI9n=
l4Uqf0D-kuZzx], reached out about working together. I=E2=80=99ve been wanti=
ng to write about this forever.=20
This essay is a Sponsored Deep Dive on Secfi. For those who are new around =
here, that means that Secfi is paying me to write about their business. You=
 can read more about how I pick and work with partners here [https://email.=
mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkU2P4yAMhn9NOUbgQEsOHEaaXY06O3sZqdo9RXw4KWoCGSBT5d8v=
bQ4r2cayZb_osdUFx5g2tcRcyCP0ZVtQBbznCUvBRNaMqfdOsSPIVvCOOMUdk0ISn_shIc7aT6q=
