et at a more mature company in exchange for a few things: a more fun work e=
nvironment, the chance to change the world, more responsibility than they&#=
8217;d get elsewhere, and a host of soft benefits, but mainly, they do it f=
or the <strong>employee stock options</strong>.&nbsp;</p><div class=3D"capt=
